import './topBar.css';
import {Container,
    Navbar,
    Row,
    Form,
    FormControl,
    Button,
} from 'react-bootstrap';

export default function TopBar() {
  return (
    <Navbar>
        <Container>
            
            <Navbar.Toggle />
            <Navbar.Collapse className="justify-content-center">
            <Navbar.Brand href="#home">EmojiBook</Navbar.Brand>
            <Form className="d-flex">
            <FormControl
                type="search"
                placeholder="Search"
                className="mr-2"
                aria-label="Search"
            />
            
            </Form>
            </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
    </Navbar>
  )
}
